  "text": "This audit identified explicit implementations of k8s.io/apiserver/pkg/storage.Interface using the Go interface compliance check pattern (var _ Interface = (*Type)(nil)). The search across kubernetes/kubernetes, etcd-io/etcd, and grafana/grafana repositories revealed one struct with an explicit interface compliance declaration: Storage in grafana/grafana at pkg/storage/unified/apistore/store.go (line 37). This struct implements the Kubernetes storage abstraction for Grafana's unified storage system, demonstrating how external organizations adopt the core Kubernetes storage interface for their own API server implementations. While kubernetes/kubernetes contains implementations of this interface (notably in staging/src/k8s.io/apiserver/pkg/storage/etcd3/store.go with the 'store' struct, and in staging/src/k8s.io/apiserver/pkg/storage/cacher/cacher.go with the 'Cacher' struct), these do not use the explicit var _ compliance check pattern. Similarly, etcd-io/etcd does not contain explicit implementations of the apiserver storage.Interface."
}

